&gt; &gt;&gt; of a
&gt; &gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; specification and
&gt; &gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; testing tool than a design tool - but it could
&gt; &gt;&gt; be a
&gt; &gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; very nice
&gt; &gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; complement to TDD to document /general rules/
&gt; &gt;&gt; rather
&gt; &gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; than /specific
